##### Notes

###### 1 General
    
*   This is an eprint of the Auckland Harbour Board and Takapuna Borough Council Empowering Act 1923\. The eprint incorporates all the amendments to the Act as at 1 November 2010\. The list of amendments at the end of these notes specifies all the amendments incorporated into this eprint since 3 September 2007\.
    
    Relevant provisions of any amending enactments that contain transitional, savings, or application provisions that cannot be compiled in the eprint are also included, after the principal enactment, in chronological order.

###### 2 About this eprint
    
*   This eprint has not been officialised. For more information about eprints and officialisation, please _see_ [http://www.pco.parliament.govt.nz/eprints/][11] ![](/images/external_link.gif).

###### 3 List of amendments incorporated in this eprint (most recent first)
    
*   Local Government (Auckland Transitional Provisions) Act 2010 (2010 No 37): [section 113(1)][10]



